verbose_text: The expression levels of FGF21, p-FGFR1 and p-ERK1/2 significantly increased in H9c2 cells transfected with pcDNA4-FGF21 compared with those transfected with an empty vector (XREF_FIG), indicating that FGF21 may positively regulate the expression level of p-FGFR1 and p-ERK1/2 to attenuate ER stress induced injury.
